metadata.name: The King of Diamond Apes 1/5000
metadata.description:
Don't miss the chance to own The King of Diamond Apes, the most coveted NFT in the jungle, as he presides over his loyal subjects with regal grace and power. With his diamond-studded crown and fierce gaze, he is sure to be the crowning jewel in any NFT collection.

This limited collection of only 5000 NFTs featuring Diamond Apes is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to own a piece of history for free. Don't miss your chance to own one of these rare and valuable NFTs, as they are sure to become highly sought-after and a prized possession in any digital art collection.
